video.title: Power Rangers Mystic Force
video.synopsis: When the wicked Undead Army is unleashed, sorceress Udonna empowers five teenagers -- the Mystic Force Power Rangers -- to save mankind.

episodes.synopsis: A spell has been broken and evil is emerging to destroy the Earth.
episodes.title: Broken Spell: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Xander, Vida, Chip and Madison finally tap into their Mystic Force powers. But without a Red Ranger, Udonna and Clare know they are in trouble.
episodes.title: Broken Spell: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Chip and Vida think they can learn more spell codes by doing community service, but they learn that real heroes are born in the face of danger.
episodes.title: Code Busters

episodes.synopsis: Nick thinks Madison is too shy. When she gets turned to stone, Nick finds out he's wrong.
episodes.title: Rock Solid

episodes.synopsis: Koragg battles the Rangers and steals their Megazord power.
episodes.title: Whispering Voices

episodes.synopsis: While in battle, Nick is whisked away with Catastros to another dimension. He must face his fears of Catastros.
episodes.title: Legendary Catastros

episodes.synopsis: Xander thinks he knows how to be a leader. But when it comes to getting the Fire Heart before Necrolai, Xander has to follow in order to lead.
episodes.title: Fire Heart

episodes.synopsis: DJ Fly, a new DJ, comes to town. Chip finds out that DJ Fly is turning the teens of Briarwood into vampires.
episodes.title: Stranger Within: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Fly Trap has been destroyed, but Vida is still a vampire. The Rangers find out that Necrolai is the vampire who bit Vida.
episodes.title: Stranger Within: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Xander has a big zit. He thinks he can get rid of it by using a perfection potion. Instead, he starts turning into a tree.
episodes.title: Petrified Xander

episodes.synopsis: Clare takes on the legacy of her mother as the Gatekeeper. Koragg captures Udonna. Necrolai is about to destroy the Rangers.
episodes.title: The Gatekeeper: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The gates have been raised and Morticon is set free. Nick goes to save Clare while the others hold off Morticon.
episodes.title: The Gatekeeper: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Necrolai gets the Rangers to break the force field of a magical cave. Inside the cave are a magical lamp and a petrified mummy.
episodes.title: Scaredy Cat

episodes.synopsis: Imperious turns into Calindor and tries to convince Udonna that he can help Mystic Force. The Rangers are busy trying to fight Jester.
episodes.title: Long Ago

episodes.synopsis: Daggeron teaches Xander that without practice, he can cause harm to the rest of the Rangers.
episodes.title: Inner Strength

episodes.synopsis: Koragg decides it's time to fight Solaris Knight. Gnatu steals life force from civilians when the Rangers come to stop him.
episodes.title: Soul Specter

episodes.synopsis: Jenji gets jealous of Fire Heart. He takes Fire Heart to live in the forest. When he goes back to find him, Fire Heart is gone.
episodes.title: Ranger Down

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers get lazy and use their magic for everything. When fighting becomes too tiring for them, the Rangers want to use Jenji.
episodes.title: Dark Wish: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Imperious has wished the Power Rangers away. The world has lost its color and evil now rules.
episodes.title: Dark Wish: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: The Tribunal of Magic has turned down the teens' request to restore things to the way they were.
episodes.title: Dark Wish: Part 3

episodes.synopsis: Imperious makes Koragg stand trial for his countless failures. In the end, Koragg argues that he fights with honor.
episodes.title: Koragg's Trial

episodes.synopsis: Daggeron and Udonna finally tell the Rangers the full story of the Great War.
episodes.title: Heir Apparent: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Koragg was really Leanbow all this time. Nick finds out he's really Leanbow and Udonna's son.
episodes.title: Heir Apparent: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: With Udonna gone, Mystic Force faces a new terror. Ten Terrors rise against the Rangers. Magma is the first Terror the Rangers must face.
episodes.title: The Light

episodes.synopsis: Oculus is chosen to capture the Light. He is able to take all the other Rangers down one by one.
episodes.title: The Hunter

episodes.synopsis: Nick and Vida keep arguing. As stubborn as they are, they need to learn to work together in order to save the others from Serpentina.
episodes.title: Hard Heads

episodes.synopsis: Leanbow is stopping the Master from rising and Sculpin has a plan to stop him.
episodes.title: The Snow Prince

episodes.synopsis: Hekatoid has captured Udonna, and the Rangers chase after him in his own dimension in order to rescue Nick's mom.
episodes.title: Light Source: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The teens lose their power trying to save Udonna.
episodes.title: Light Source: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Matoombo is chosen to bring forth the Master. But Matoombo doesn't want to hurt anyone. Vida teams up with him to try to seal the Master away forever.
episodes.title: The Return

episodes.synopsis: Itassis doesn't want to fight for the Master anymore and defies his wishes. The Master takes matters into his own hands and destroys Mystic Mother.
episodes.title: Mystic Fate: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: With Daggeron and Leanbow defeated, the Rangers must use all their magic to try to save both the Surface World and the Magical Realm.
episodes.title: Mystic Fate: Part 2
